News.Title: Supreme Facility Management Partners with Komorebi Tech Solutions for Mumbai Bus Services
News.Summary: Supreme Facility Management has announced a strategic partnership with Komorebi Tech Solutions Pvt Ltd to improve bus services in the Mumbai Metropolitan Region. This collaboration is anticipated to generate a business potential of approximately 42 crore rupees.

News.Title: Supreme Facility Management: Shares List at 1.3% Discount on NSE SME
News.Summary: Supreme Facility Management shares debuted on NSE SME at ₹75.00, a 1.32% discount to the IPO price of ₹76. The IPO raised ₹50 crore and was oversubscribed 27.01 times. The company plans to use proceeds for working capital, inorganic growth, and general corporate purposes.
